com.att.research.xacml.std.pip.engines.csv

Interface CSVResolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ConfigurableResolver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ConfigurableCSVResolver

    public interface CSVResolver
extends ConfigurableResolver
    CSVResolver is the interface used by the CSVEngine to create list of column parameters to check for XACML attribute requests and convert the results into XACML attributes.
    Author:
    pameladragosh
